data.title: Eagles' Julio Jones promoted to active roster, expected to play vs. Dolphins
data.meta_description: The Philadelphia Eagles have elevated wide receiver Julio Jones from their practice roster and he is expected to play against the Miami Dolphins on Sunday, the team announced Saturday.
